## Introduction

This is the second year Univerity projected built in a team of 6 people. We were challenged to go though a lot of sessions with client and build:

- Requirement Analysis
- Data Models
- Figma UX/UI designs
- Code using php laravel
- Deploy on [combell](https://www.combell.com/en/)
